title: Turkey earthquake: Aleppo among worst-hit areas in Syria
description: More than 1,000 people have been killed in Syria after a huge earthquake struck neighbouring Turkey.
content:
Syria's war-torn city of Aleppo is among the areas to have borne the brunt of a deadly earthquake, which also devastated parts of southern Turkey.
